aristaPfcMIB.name: aristaPfcMIB
aristaPfcMIB.contactinfo: Arista Networks, Inc. Postal: 5453 Great America Parkway Santa Clara, CA 95054 Tel: +1 408 547-5500 E-mail: snmp@arista.com
aristaPfcMIB.description: Extensions for managing IEEE 802.1Qbb Priority-based Flow Control on Arista devices. This module extends IEEE8021-PFC-MIB by providing per class-of-service information for the supported Arista platforms.

AristaPfcCOSIndex.name: AristaPfcCOSIndex
AristaPfcCOSIndex.description: A unique value for each Ethernet class-of-service priority

aristaPfcPriorityTable.name: aristaPfcPriorityTable
aristaPfcPriorityTable.description: This table contains the per class-of-service priority-flow-control information of an interface.

aristaPfcPriorityEntry.name: aristaPfcPriorityEntry
aristaPfcPriorityEntry.description: A list of attributes of each ingress class-of-service of an interface.

aristaPfcIfIndex.name: aristaPfcIfIndex
aristaPfcIfIndex.description: The interface identified by a particular value of this index is the same interface as identified by the same value of ifIndex.

aristaPfcPriorityIndex.name: aristaPfcPriorityIndex
aristaPfcPriorityIndex.description: The Ethernet class-of-service index for accessing the per-priority information of an interface.

aristaPfcPriorityRequests.name: aristaPfcPriorityRequests
aristaPfcPriorityRequests.description: A count of the invoked PFC M_CONTROL.request primitives with this priority class asserted. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system, and at other times as indicated by the value of ifCounterDiscontinuityTime.

aristaPfcPriorityIndications.name: aristaPfcPriorityIndications
aristaPfcPriorityIndications.description: A count of the received PFC M_CONTROL.indication primitives with this priority class asserted. Discontinuities in the value of this counter can occur at re-initialization of the management system, and at other times as indicated by the value of ifCounterDiscontinuityTime.

aristaPfcCompliance.name: aristaPfcCompliance
aristaPfcCompliance.description: The compliance statement for Arista switches that support Priority Flow Control (PFC).

aristaPfcGroup.name: aristaPfcGroup
aristaPfcGroup.description: The group of required PFC objects.
